column2: SELECT    m.id as [id], str(m.ra,#,#) AS ra, str(m.dec,#,#) AS dec,     sp.plate, sp.fiberid, sp.mjd, sp.z, sp.zwarning,     g.Flux_Hb_#, g.Flux_Hb_#_Err,   g.Flux_OIII_#, g.Flux_OIII_#_Err,   g.Flux_OI_#, g.Flux_OI_#_Err,   g.Flux_SII_#, g.Flux_SII_#_Err, g.Flux_SII_#,g.Flux_SII_#_Err,     g.Flux_NII_#, g.Flux_NII_#_Err, g.Flux_OII_#, g.Flux_OII_#_Err,g.Flux_OII_#,g.Flux_OII_#_Err,   g.Flux_Ha_#, g.Flux_Ha_#_Err, g.bpt  into mydb.res_xshaped_lineinfo_best2 from MyDB.sdss_in_finalbestXRGs_lineinfo AS m             OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n     LEFT JOIN PhotoObj AS sp ON n.objid=sp.objid     LEFT OUTER JOIN SpecPhotoAll  AS po ON po.objID=sp.objID     LEFT OUTER JOIN emissionLinesPort as g ON g.specObjID = sp.specObjID     LEFT OUTER JOIN photoZ pp ON pp.objID = sp.objID    ORDER by m.id
